task.summary: * Piece contains now its position (Point) * Grid is no longer a Matrix, but a collection of Piece. The methods 'get(x, y)' and 'add(piece)' change this level of abstraction to be easier to manipulate a grid ; however, it might be not compatible with the MVC model... * Added IntelliJ annotations, and changed all @/@Nullable to IntelliJ's * Shape has an untested method 'trim' to trim the dimension. * PieceController is bugged because it is not compatible with the new grid yet. * Square is now deprecated. It will be removed soon.
